 | title = Are Standard Solar Models Reliable?
 | journal = Physical Review Letters
 | year = January 1997
 | volume = 78
 | issue = 2
 | pages = 171–174
 | doi = 10.1103/PhysRevLett.78.171
 | id = 
 | bibcode = 1997PhRvL..78..171B
|arxiv = astro-ph/9610250 }}</ref> 日震學揭示的特性包括外側的對流層和內側的輻射層以不同的速度旋轉，這引發太陽[[發電機|發電機]]產生磁場效應的想法<ref name="Thompson2003">{{cite journal
